'''亞美尼亞解放祕密軍'''（ASALA；{{lang-hy|Հայաստանի Ազատագրութեան Հայ Գաղտնի Բանակ／ՀԱՀԳԲ|Hayasdani Azadakrut'ean Hay Kaghdni Panag／HAHKP}}）是[[亞美尼亞人|亞美尼亞人]]在[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]建立的[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100622030256/http://www.nps.edu/Library/Research/SubjectGuides/SpecialTopics/TerroristProfile/Prior/ASALA.html|title=ARMENIAN SECRET ARMY FOR THE LIBERATION OF ARMENIA (ASALA)|publisher=Naval Postgraduate School}}</ref><ref name="wievorka">{{Cite book | last = Wieviorka | first = Michel | title = The Making of Terrorism | year = 1993 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=pLR_CMUas3gC&pg=PA256 | pages = 256 | isbn = 0-226-89650-1 | quote = ''Nationalist with no qualms about attacking its own community, Marxist-Leninist without a social base, ASALA was, in a word, a classic terrorist group, the product of an inversion.'' | access-date = 2020-12-31 | archive-date = 2021-01-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013039/https://books.google.com/books?id=pLR_CMUas3gC&pg=PA256 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia|title= Armenian Secret Army for the Liberation of Armenia|encyclopedia= Britannica|year= 2011|publisher= Encyclopædia Britannica|url= https://www.britannica.com/topic/Armenian-Secret-Army-for-the-Liberation-of-Armenia|access-date= 2020-12-31|archive-date= 2021-01-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013034/https://www.britannica.com/topic/Armenian-Secret-Army-for-the-Liberation-of-Armenia|dead-url= no}}</ref>，意識形態為{{le|反土耳其|Anti-Turkish sentiment}}與[[馬克思主義|馬克思主義]]<ref>{{Cite book|last=Fuller, Graham E., 1937-|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/27676707|title=Turkey's new geopolitics : from the Balkans to Western China|date=1993|publisher=Westview Press|others=Lesser, Ian O., 1957-, Henze, Paul B., 1924-2011., Brown, J. F. (James F.), 1928-2009.|isbn=0-8133-8659-4|location=Boulder|oclc=27676707|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013047/https://www.worldcat.org/title/turkeys-new-geopolitics-from-the-balkans-to-western-china/oclc/27676707|dead-url=no}}</ref>，活躍於1975年<ref name="hunsicker">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=K4XefrTlSygC&q=%22to+compel+the+Turkish+Government+to+acknowledge+publicly+its+alleged+responsibility+for+the+Armenian+Genocide+in+1915,+pay+reparations,+and+cede+territory+for+an+Armenian+homeland%22&pg=PA431|title=Understanding International Counter Terrorism|publisher=Universal-Publishers|last=Hunsicker|isbn=1-58112-905-X|pages=431|year=2006|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013059/https://books.google.com/books?id=K4XefrTlSygC&q=%22to+compel+the+Turkish+Government+to+acknowledge+publicly+its+alleged+responsibility+for+the+Armenian+Genocide+in+1915%2C+pay+reparations%2C+and+cede+territory+for+an+Armenian+homeland%22&pg=PA431|dead-url=no}}</ref>至1990年代間<ref>Roy, Olivier. ''Turkey Today: A European Nation?'' p. 170. Roy suggests that the Orly incident led to "dissension end[ing] in the settling of scores in which ASALA militants killed each other in their camp at Bekaa (Al-Biqa, Lebanon)... (It) practically disappeared. It resurfaced once again, however, to assassinate important members of the Lebanese section of the Dashnak Party (March 1985 – May 1986)."</ref>，後來該組織不再進行恐怖活動，但據稱仍持續運作至今<ref>{{Cite web|title=ASALA member dies in car accident in Lebanon|url=https://news.am/eng/news/601572.html|access-date=2020-12-28|website=news.am|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013056/https://news.am/eng/news/601572.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=AA|first=DAILY SABAH WITH|date=2020-09-28|title=Armenia deploys PKK, ASALA terrorists to occupied areas, Azerbaijan's envoy to Ankara says|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/politics/diplomacy/armenia-deploys-pkk-asala-terrorists-to-occupied-areas-azerbaijans-envoy-to-ankara-says|access-date=2020-12-28|website=Daily Sabah|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013026/https://www.dailysabah.com/politics/diplomacy/armenia-deploys-pkk-asala-terrorists-to-occupied-areas-azerbaijans-envoy-to-ankara-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞美尼亞解放祕密軍被許多人視為恐怖組織<ref name="jessup">{{Cite book |last=Jessup |year=1998 |title=An Encyclopedic Dictionary of Conflict and Conflict Resolution, 1945-1996 |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group |isbn=0-313-28112-2 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jh3Q5F7BaB8C&pg=PA39 |pages=39 |quote=''A leftist separatist terrorist group that, before 1984, was quite active in the European area, ASALA began its operations before 1975.'' |access-date=2020-12-31 |archive-date=2021-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013059/https://books.google.com/books?id=jh3Q5F7BaB8C&pg=PA39 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{ISBN|0-313-28112-2}}, {{ISBN|978-0-313-28112-9}}, p. 39</ref><ref>Michel Wieviorka, David Gordon White. The making of terrorism. University of Chicago Press, 1993. {{ISBN|0-226-89650-1}}, {{ISBN|978-0-226-89650-2}}, p. 256</ref><ref>Bruce Hoffman. Inside terrorism. Columbia University Press, 2006. {{ISBN|0-231-12699-9}}, {{ISBN|978-0-231-12699-1}}, p. 71</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Göçek |first1=Fatma Müge |title=The Transformation of Turkey: Redefining State and the Society from the Ottoman Empire to the Modern Era |date=2011 |publisher=I.B. Tauris |page=151}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldstatesmen.org/Terrorist.html#Armenian|title=Terrorist Organizations|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2013-01-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DnlbhFvH?url=http://www.worldstatesmen.org/Terrorist.html#Armenian|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也有人將其視為[[游擊隊|游擊隊]]<ref>Political dissent: an international guide to dissident, extra-parliamentary, guerrilla, and illegal political movements, by Henry W. Degenhardt, Alan John Day, Gale Research Company, 1983, p. 489</ref><ref>''Remembering with Vengeance'', by {{tsl|en|Pico Iyer||Pico Iyer}} – ''[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]'', № 32, 8 August 1983</ref><ref>The Caucasus: an introduction, by Frederik Coene, 2009 – 238 pages, p. 221</ref><ref>The history of Turkey, by Douglas Arthur Howard – 2001 – 241 pages, p. 161</ref>或武裝組織<ref>Untold Histories of the Middle East, by Amy Singer, Christoph Neumann, Selcuk Somel – 2010 – 240 pages, p. 27</ref>，1980年代[[美國|美國]]政府亦視其為恐怖組織<ref>United States Department of State. [http://www.hsdl.org/?view&did=481506 Patterns of Global Terrorism Report: 1989] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hsdl.org/?view&did=481506 |date=20140219060141 }}, p 57</ref>。亞美尼亞解放祕密軍所執行的攻擊、暗殺行動共造成46人死亡、299人受傷。該組織在西亞、歐洲與美國共執行了超過50起爆炸案<ref>{{Cite web|title=27 May 1988|url=https://www.upi.com/Archives/1988/05/27/Terrorists-claim-leaders-murder-solved/5154580708800/|access-date=20 October 2020|website=United Press International|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013026/https://www.upi.com/Archives/1988/05/27/Terrorists-claim-leaders-murder-solved/5154580708800/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

亞美尼亞解放祕密軍自稱其宗旨為促使[[土耳其|土耳其]]政府承認1915年的[[亚美尼亚种族灭绝|亚美尼亚种族灭绝]]、賠償與割讓土地<ref>{{Cite book | title = Patterns of Global Terrorism Report – 1996 | chapter = Appendix B | author = U.S. Department of State| title-link = s:Patterns of Global Terrorism Report/1996 }}</ref>，其目標為結合曾屬[[鄂圖曼帝國|鄂圖曼帝國]]的[[西亞美尼亞|西亞美尼亞]]與[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的[[亞美尼亞蘇維埃社會主義共和國|亞美尼亞蘇維埃社會主義共和國]]，建立[[大亞美尼亞|大亞美尼亞]]<ref name="Terrorist Group Profiles 1989. p. 32">Terrorist Group Profiles. DIANE Publishing, 1989. p. 32</ref>，該組織認為[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]後的《[[塞夫尔条约|塞夫尔条约]]》中，[[美國總統|美國總統]][[伍德羅·威爾遜|伍德羅·威爾遜]]劃給亞美尼亞的土地（[[威爾遜亞美尼亞|威爾遜亞美尼亞]]）應屬亞美尼亞<ref>{{cite book|author=Pitman, Paul M. |title=Turkey: A Country Study|publisher=The Federal Research Division of the Library of Congress|page= 283, 354–355|oclc=17841957}}</ref>。

亞美尼亞解放祕密軍受到歐洲、美國等地的[[亞美尼亞僑民|亞美尼亞僑民]]暗中支持<ref>Encyclopedia of terrorism. Harvey W. Kushner. SAGE, 2003. p. 47</ref>。1990年代起組織可能因內部發生分裂且缺乏資金而不再活躍，最後一起攻擊是1997年一群自稱該組織的人員在[[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]的土耳其大使館執行了爆炸案<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fas.org/irp/threat/terror_97/eurasia.html|title=Patterns of Global Terrorism: 1997: Europe and Eurasia Overview|last=Federation of American Scientists|website=FAS|access-date=April 11, 2019|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411155351/https://fas.org/irp/threat/terror_97/eurasia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該組織的口號有「武力鬥爭和正確的政治路線是亞美尼亞的道路」與「被壓迫人民的革命聯盟萬歲」<ref>{{cite news|author= G. Yazchian|title= Thirty years ago this day was born ASALA|newspaper=Azg daily|date=2005-01-20|language=hy}}</ref>。

==建立==
[[File:United_Armenia.png|thumb]]的範圍]]
1965年，世界各地的[[亞美尼亞人|亞美尼亞人]]紀念[[亚美尼亚种族灭绝|亚美尼亚种族灭绝]]50週年，[[土耳其|土耳其]]一貫[[對亞美尼亞種族滅絕的否認|不承認]]亚美尼亚种族灭绝曾經發生，在和平的抗爭無效後，一些亞美尼亞人改採更激烈的手段<ref>{{cite book|author=Paul Moussault (red.) & Barbara Sahakian|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zXZ_rgEACAAJ&dq=ASALA+de+Nemesis+voor+de+Armeense+genocide.+Stadsguerrilla+tegen+Turkije&hl=ru&sa=X&redir_esc=y |title=“ASALA de Nemesis voor de Armeense genocide. Stadsguerrilla tegen Turkije (1975–1988)”|year=2015|ISBN=9789067283076}}</ref>。1973年，一位亞美尼亞大屠殺的倖存者{{le|古爾根·亞尼基安|Gourgen Yanikian}}在美國[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]槍殺了兩名土耳其外交官<ref name="JCSS">{{Cite book | last = Kurz & Merari | first = Anat & Ariel | title = JCSS Study No. 2 ASALA – Irrational Terror or Political Tool | work=The Jerusalem Post | year = 1985 | location = Jerusalem | pages = 3 | isbn = 0-8133-0324-9|quote= The ideology informing ASALA's activities is therefore nationalistic and leftist, with a strong accent on motives such as revenge on Turkey, and on forcing the world to recognize the historic injustice inflicted on the Armenians.}}</ref>。1975年（亚美尼亚种族灭绝60週年），{{tsl|en|Hagop Hagopian (guerilla)|哈戈普·哈戈皮安}}、{{le|詹姆士·卡努西安|James Karnusian}}<ref>Rev. James Karnusian, retired pastor and one of three persons to establish ASALA, dies in Switzerland // The Armenian Reporter International, 18 April 1998.</ref>與{{le|凱沃爾克·阿杰米恩|Kevork Ajemian}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104104042/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-22427363.html |title=Kevork Ajemian, Prominent Contemporary Writer and Surviving Member of Triumvirate Which Founded ASALA, Dies in Beirut, Lebanon|publisher=Armenian Reporter|date=1999-02-01}}</ref>在一些[[巴勒斯坦人|巴勒斯坦人]]的幫助下<ref name="countrystudy">"{{cite book|url=http://countrystudies.us/turkey/|title=Turkey: A Country Study|author=Helen Chapin Metz|publisher=The Federal Research Division of the Library of Congress|page=283, 354–355|oclc=17841957|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2011-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722203451/http://countrystudies.us/turkey/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於甫爆發[[黎巴嫩內戰|內戰]]的[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]][[貝魯特|貝魯特]]建立了「亞美尼亞解放祕密軍」<ref name=":13">{{Cite book|title=Armenian terrorism : the past, the present, the prospects|last=Hyland, Francis P.|date=1991|publisher=Westview Press|oclc=466448724}}</ref>，最初以「囚徒古爾根·亞尼基安組織」（The Prisoner Kurken Yanikian Group）為名<ref>{{cite book|title=Near East/South Asia Report|author=United States Foreign Broadcast Information Service|publisher= United States Joint Publications Research Service|year= 1987|page=3}}</ref>，許多成員為{{le|亞美尼亞裔黎巴嫩人|Lebanese-Armenians}}<ref>Roy, Olivier. ''Turkey Today: A European Nation?'' p. 169.</ref>，組織的最高領導人為亞美尼亞人民總司令（General Command of the People of Armenia；VAN）<ref>The Middle East Annual: Issues & Events, 1984, edited by David H. Partington, p. 155</ref>。

亞美尼亞解放祕密軍策劃的活動主要是針對土耳其外交官與政要的攻擊<ref name="countrystudy" />。其主要政治訴求有二，一是促使土耳其政府承認亚美尼亚种族灭绝並承擔責任，二是以武力統一亞美尼亞人曾控制的土地，建立[[大亞美尼亞|大亞美尼亞]]，並確立[[科學社會主義|科學社會主義]]為亞美尼亞的主要意識形態<ref name="Terrorist Group Profiles 1989. p. 32" />。1983年，該組織曾表示它們支持[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]，希望獲得其他蘇聯加盟國的支持，共同對抗土耳其的殖民主義<ref name=":13"/>。

==盟友==
巴勒斯坦的左翼組織[[解放巴勒斯坦人民陣線|解放巴勒斯坦人民陣線]]為亞美尼亞解放祕密軍的盟友，有消息指後者創始人之一的哈戈普·哈戈皮安年少時曾加入該組織<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gunter|first=Michael M.|date=2007|title=Armenian Terrorism: A Reappraisal|url=https://journals.lib.unb.ca/index.php/JCS/article/view/10546|journal=Journal of Conflict Studies|language=en|volume=27|issue=2|issn=1715-5673|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013105/https://journals.lib.unb.ca/index.php/JCS/article/view/10546|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並得到「戰士」（Mujahed）的稱號<ref name=":13"/>。哈戈皮安一向同情巴勒斯坦人，後來亞美尼亞解放秘密軍也與[[巴勒斯坦解放組織|巴勒斯坦解放組織]]一起受訓<ref>{{Cite book|title=Transnational sources of support for Armenian terrorism|last=Gunter, Michael M.|oclc=36960193}}</ref>。

===可能的盟友===
有消息指亞美尼亞解放祕密軍曾與[[庫德斯坦工人黨|庫德斯坦工人黨]]、[[红色旅|赤軍旅]]與[[埃塔|埃塔]]等歐洲、亞洲的左翼組織往來<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP85T00283R000400030009-2.pdf|title=The Armenian Secret Army for the Liberation of Armenia: A Continuing International Threat|last=Central Intelligence Agency|date=1984|access-date=April 11, 2019|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101012939/https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP85T00283R000400030009-2.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外該組織還與{{le|亞美尼亞種族滅絕正義突擊隊|Justice Commandos of the Armenian Genocide}}（JCAG）有聯繫，後者為一[[右翼|右翼]]組織，也常對土耳其外交官發動襲擊，與亞美尼亞解放祕密軍一樣要求土耳其承認亚美尼亚种族灭绝<ref name=":02" />，不過相較於亞美尼亞解放祕密軍支持蘇聯、接受亞美尼亞的蘇聯加盟國身分<ref name=":13"/>，JCAG的目標為建立一個獨立的亞美尼亞國<ref name=":03">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP85T00283R000400030009-2.pdf|title=The Armenian Secret Army for the Liberation of Armenia: A Continuing International Threat|last=Central Intelligence Agency|date=1984|access-date=April 11, 2019|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101012939/https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP85T00283R000400030009-2.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以攻擊型態論，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍較常使用[[炸藥|炸藥]]，據統計在其發動的186起攻擊中，有146起均使用炸藥，僅有33起使用槍械<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/Results.aspx?charttype=pie&chart=weapon&casualties_type=&casualties_max=&perpetrator=305|title=GTD Search Results|website=www.start.umd.edu|access-date=2019-05-10|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013104/https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/Results.aspx?charttype=pie&chart=weapon&casualties_type=&casualties_max=&perpetrator=305|dead-url=no}}</ref>；JCAG則較常使用槍械，在其發動的47起攻擊中只有23起使用炸藥，而有26起使用槍械<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/Results.aspx?charttype=pie&chart=weapon&casualties_type=&casualties_max=&perpetrator=3292|title=GTD Search Results|website=www.start.umd.edu|access-date=2019-05-10|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205165353/https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/Results.aspx?charttype=pie&chart=weapon&casualties_type=&casualties_max=&perpetrator=3292}}</ref>。

==攻擊==
[[File:ASALA_memorial_in_Yerablur.jpg|thumb]][[耶拉伯勒軍人公墓|耶拉伯勒軍人公墓]]中的亞美尼亞解放祕密軍紀念碑]]
據{{le|預防恐怖主義全國紀念協會|National Memorial Institute for the Prevention of Terrorism}}（MIPT）統計，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍共執行了84起攻擊，造成46人死亡與299人受傷<ref name="MIPT">{{cite web |url=http://www.tkb.org/Group.jsp?groupID=258 |title=MIPT Terrorism Knowledge Base |date=15 November 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071115020146/http://www.tkb.org/Group.jsp?groupID=258 |archive-date=2007-11-15 |accessdate=2020-12-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1975年，{{le|土耳其駐奧地利大使|Turkish Ambassador to Austria}}{{le|達尼士·圖納勒吉爾|Daniş Tunalıgil}}被暗殺，兩日後{{le|土耳其駐法國大使|Turkish Ambassador to France}}{{le|伊斯梅尔·埃雷兹|İsmail Erez}}也被暗殺。亞美尼亞解放祕密軍與亞美尼亞種族滅絕正義突擊隊均宣稱作案。1980年，{{le|亞歷山大·耶尼科姆西揚|Alexander Yenikomshian}}與蘇茲·馬謝來吉安（Suzy Mahseredjian）在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[日內瓦|日內瓦]]的一家酒店策劃爆炸案時炸彈意外爆炸而被捕，為第一批被逮捕的亞美尼亞解放祕密軍成員<ref>Le Combat armenien: entre terrorisme et utopie : Lausanne, 1923–1983, by Armand Gaspard, L'AGE D'HOMME, 1984, p. 72</ref>。

1981年9月24日，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍{{tsl|en|1981 Turkish consulate attack in Paris|1981年巴黎土耳其大使館攻擊|襲擊巴黎的土耳其大使館}}，挾持56名人質約15小時，要求土耳其釋放12名[[政治犯|政治犯]]（兩名亞美尼亞人、五名土耳其人與五名庫德人）<ref>Guerilla threat to kill 40 in Paris siege, [[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]], Sep. 25, 1981, p. 3</ref>，轉播事件的電視新聞[[收視率|收視率]]是該年度法國節目中數一數二的<ref>Children of Armenia, by M. Bobelian, Simon & Schuster, 2009, p. 159</ref>。1982年8月7日[[安卡拉|安卡拉]][[埃森博阿國際機場攻擊|埃森博阿國際機場的襲擊]]是亞美尼亞解放祕密軍發動最著名的攻擊之一，也是該組織首次對非外交官的平民發動攻擊，兩名武裝分子在擁擠的候機室內對群眾開火，共造成9人死亡，72人受傷。1983年7月15日，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍在[[巴黎|巴黎]][[奧利機場|奧利機場]]{{tsl|en|1983 Orly Airport attack|1983年奧利機場攻擊|發動攻擊}}，在[[土耳其航空|土耳其航空]]的櫃檯將一行李箱中的炸彈引爆，造成8人死亡，55人受傷，傷亡者大都不是土耳其人<ref>Brian Forst, Jack R. Greene, James P. Lynch. Criminologists on Terrorism and Homeland Security. Cambridge University Press, 2011. {{ISBN|0521899451}}, 9780521899451, p. 431</ref><ref>Council of Europe, Documents, Vol. 1, May 1984, Report by Amadei, p. 9</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/IncidentSummary.aspx?gtdid=198307150003|title=Incident Summary for GTDID: 198307150003|website=www.start.umd.edu|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023073736/https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/IncidentSummary.aspx?gtdid=198307150003|dead-url=no}}</ref>。是次攻擊造成了該組織內部的分裂，部分成員認為此案造成了反效果<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hetq.am/eng/society/7332/ |access-date=2008-09-02 |title=He Was a Man Deeply Connected to the Natural World |work=Hetq Online |date=2007-11-26 |first=Edik |last=Baghdasaryan |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090522021904/http://hetq.am/eng/society/7332/ |archive-date=2009-05-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，組織分裂成哈戈皮安領導的亞美尼亞解放祕密軍激進派（ASALA-Militant）與1980年加入組織的亞美尼亞裔美國人[[蒙捷·梅爾科尼揚|蒙捷·梅爾科尼揚]]領導的亞美尼亞解放祕密軍革命運動（ASALA-Mouvement Révolutionnaire）<ref>{{cite book|author=Harvey W. Kushner|title=Encyclopedia of terrorism|publisher=SAGE|year=2002|ISBN=0-7619-2408-6|page=47}}</ref>{{Notetag|1=兩派人馬不和已久，組織分裂的另一導火線是哈戈皮安的兩名下屬在黎巴嫩的一軍營被反對者暗殺<ref name="Pluchinsky2020">{{cite book|author=Dennis A Pluchinsky|title=Anti-american Terrorism: From Eisenhower To Trump - A Chronicle Of The Threat And Response: Volume Ii: The Reagan And George H.w. Bush Administrations|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GGjvDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA189|date=18 June 2020|publisher=World Scientific Publishing Company|isbn=978-1-78634-793-0|pages=189|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205165408/https://books.google.com/books?id=GGjvDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA189|dead-url=no}}</ref>。}}。1981年大使館襲擊後，法國內政部長{{le|加斯東·德費爾|Gaston Defferre}}稱此行動為「正義」，且四名犯案的亞美尼亞人均獲得輕判，一度有傳言指法國政府和亞美尼亞解放祕密軍有秘密協議<ref name=echiksom>{{cite web|author=Echikson, William|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/csmonitor_historic/access/260828642.html?dids=260828642:260828642&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&date=Jul+19%2C+1983&author=By+William+Echikson+Special+to+The+Christian+Science+Monitor&pub=Christian+Science+Monitor&desc=Armenian+bombing+at+Orly+ends+pact+between+Socialists+and+terrorists&pqatl=google|title=Armenian bombing at Orly ends pact between Socialists and terrorists|publisher=The Christian Science Monitor|date=1983-07-19|access-date=2021-01-01|archive-date=2012-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021051818/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/csmonitor_historic/access/260828642.html?dids=260828642:260828642&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&date=Jul+19,+1983&author=By+William+Echikson+Special+to+The+Christian+Science+Monitor&pub=Christian+Science+Monitor&desc=Armenian+bombing+at+Orly+ends+pact+between+Socialists+and+terrorists&pqatl=google}}</ref>，此次機場攻擊後法國警方迅速逮捕了嫌犯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1983/10/09/world/around-the-world-french-hold-armenians-in-orly-airport-bombing.html|title=French Hold Armenians In Orly Airport Bombing|publisher=The New York Times|date=1983-10-09|accessdate=2021-01-01|archive-date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518224423/https://www.nytimes.com/1983/10/09/world/around-the-world-french-hold-armenians-in-orly-airport-bombing.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，消除了此傳言<ref name=echiksom/>。

亞美尼亞解放祕密軍多次與歐洲政府談判以取得政治成果。該組織曾兩度停止在[[瑞士|瑞士]]發動攻擊，一次是為了使數名亞美尼亞囚犯早點被釋放，另一次則是在一名瑞士法官譴責土耳其否定亞美尼亞種族滅絕之後。1979年，該組織與[[義大利|義大利]]政府談判，宣布不在義大利發動攻擊，以換取義大利關閉協助亞美尼亞人搬離蘇聯的移民辦公室<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP85T00283R000400030009-2.pdf|title=The Armenian Secret Army for the Liberation of Armenia: A Continuing International Threat|last=Central Intelligence Agency|date=1984|access-date=April 11, 2019|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101012939/https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP85T00283R000400030009-2.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===土耳其反應===
土耳其曾指控[[塞普勒斯|塞普勒斯]]、[[希臘|希臘]]、[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]、[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]與[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]暗中資助、支持亞美尼亞解放祕密軍，但它們均無公開支持該組織<ref name="countrystudy" />。該組織的數次攻擊後，土耳其民族主義者開始攻擊其國內的{{tsl|en|Armenians in Turkey|土耳其的亞美尼亞人|亞美尼亞人}}，1979年10月12日，土耳其駐荷蘭大使在[[海牙|海牙]]被暗殺後（亞美尼亞解放祕密軍與JCAG均宣稱犯案），10月19日，[[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦堡]]的亞美尼亞教堂也受到了報復攻擊而發生爆炸<ref name="azadhye">{{cite web|author={{le|泰莎·霍夫曼|Tessa Hofmann|Tessa Hofmann}}|url=http://www.armenian.ch/asa/Docs/faae02.pdf|title=Armenians in Turkey today|accessdate=2021-01-01|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713083633/http://www.armenian.ch/asa/Docs/faae02.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1980年，土耳其政府在伊斯坦堡機場逮捕了亞美尼亞裔的牧師{{le|曼努爾·耶爾加蒂安|Manuel Yergatian}}，指控他持有將土耳其領土劃屬亞美尼亞的地圖，後來他因被控與亞美尼亞解放祕密軍有關聯而被判處14年徒刑，[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]指其為良心犯，且對他的指控毫無根據。亞美尼亞研究學者{{le|泰莎·霍夫曼|Tessa Hofmann}}指出土耳其經常以與亞美尼亞解放祕密軍合作為由將左翼反對組織的成員定罪<ref name="azadhye" />。

1982年[[埃森博阿國際機場攻擊|埃森博阿國際機場攻擊]]後，土耳其總統[[凯南·埃夫伦|凯南·埃夫伦]]頒布消滅亞美尼亞解放祕密軍的命令，由[[土耳其國家情報局|土耳其國家情報局]]下的國際行動組執行，埃夫伦的女兒即為行動的負責人之一<ref>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.aksiyon.com.tr/detay.php?id=15119 |access-date=2008-12-13 |title=Asala operasyonlarını Kenan Evren'in kızı yönetti |date=2004-09-06 |first=Faruk |last=Mercan |author-link=Faruk Mercan |volume=509 |publisher=Feza Gazetecilik A.Ş. |journal={{le|Aksiyon}} |language=tr |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060426171629/http://www.aksiyon.com.tr/detay.php?id=15119 |archive-date=2006-04-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.sabah.com.tr/2004/09/08/siy112.html |access-date=2008-12-13 |title=Evren: Kızım MİT'te çalışıyordu |date=2004-09-08 |language=tr |work=Sabah |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090616050947/http://www.sabah.com.tr/2004/09/08/siy112.html |archive-date=2009-06-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1983年國際行動組在法國與黎巴嫩分別派遣一支小隊，雇用剛出獄的{{le|雇用殺手|contract killer|殺手}}{{le|阿卜杜拉·查特莱|Abdullah Çatlı}}為法國支隊隊長（但未向其透露身份）<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://arsiv.sabah.com.tr/2007/10/17//haber,D6295FFF00984E8D827CBD646EDB8918.html |access-date=2009-01-02 |title=Çatlı'yı kullandık ve başarılı oldu |date=2007-10-17 |quote=Benim gerçek kimliğim mi? Bunu hiçbir zaman bilmedi. Bana 'Albayım' derdi, çünkü beni askerlikten ayrılmış sanıyordu |first=Ali Kemal |last=Erdem |work=Sabah |language=tr |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204081257/http://arsiv.sabah.com.tr/2007/10/17/haber%2CD6295FFF00984E8D827CBD646EDB8918.html |archive-date=2009-02-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，後來又派遣另一支由情報局人員領導的分隊；黎巴嫩小隊的成員則均為情報局與特種部隊成員，情報局人員{{le|希拉姆·阿巴斯|Hiram Abas}}為隊長<ref name="efsane">{{Cite news |url=http://arsiv.sabah.com.tr/2008/09/28/haber,B5E3B51FA2F94618A781886CB7B3B590.html |access-date=2008-12-25 |title=ASALA operasyonları efsane mi? |date=2008-09-28 |work=Sabah |first=Ecevit |last=Kilic |language=tr |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204043721/http://arsiv.sabah.com.tr/2008/09/28/haber%2CB5E3B51FA2F94618A781886CB7B3B590.html |archive-date=2008-12-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。查特莱法國支隊的許多爆炸案均失敗，他自稱成功暗殺了亞美尼亞解放祕密軍領導人哈戈皮安，但暗殺發生時查特莱正因毒品案在法國監獄服刑，法國的另一分隊則成功策劃了數起攻擊，尚不清楚黎巴嫩支隊是否策劃了任何攻擊<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://arsiv.sabah.com.tr/2008/09/28/haber,6BC4820941214D84A08DD404742B2C6F.html |access-date=2008-12-25 |title=Boş konser salonu bombalandı |date=2008-09-28 |work=Sabah |first=Ecevit |last=Kilic |language=tr |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204043711/http://arsiv.sabah.com.tr/2008/09/28/haber%2C6BC4820941214D84A08DD404742B2C6F.html |archive-date=2008-12-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==解散==
1982年[[第五次以阿戰爭|以色列入侵黎巴嫩]]後，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍失去了許多支持，組織也受到相當影響，被迫撤離位於貝魯特的總部<ref name="Pluchinsky2020"/>，其過去的盟友[[巴勒斯坦解放組織|巴勒斯坦解放組織]]撤回支持，並轉而向法國情報單位提供關於亞美尼亞解放祕密軍的情報。1988年4月28日，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍的創始者與領導人{{tsl|en|Hagop Hagopian (guerilla)|哈戈普·哈戈皮安}}在[[希臘|希臘]][[雅典|雅典]]一個富有的社區被槍殺<ref>Melkonian, Markar. ''My Brother's Road: An American's Fateful Journey to Armenia''. New York: Palgrave Macmillan, 2005 pg. 187.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.apnewsarchive.com/1988/Gunmen-Kill-Man-in-Athens-Identified-as-Armenian-Terrorist-Chief/id-e2d5254813247e3cc55ad77b542b392b|title=Gunmen Kill Man in Athens Identified as Armenian Terrorist Chief|date=28 April 1988|work=Associated Press News Archive|publisher=The Associated Press|access-date=15 September 2012|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104010/http://www.apnewsarchive.com/1988/Gunmen-Kill-Man-in-Athens-Identified-as-Armenian-Terrorist-Chief/id-e2d5254813247e3cc55ad77b542b392b|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[土耳其國家情報局|土耳其國家情報局]]表示哈戈皮安被殺後，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍即告解散，另外有土耳其消息指{{tsl|en|1983 Orly Airport attack|1983年奧利機場攻擊}}後，許多海外亞美尼亞人停止了對亞美尼亞解放祕密軍的資助，使其無法繼續運作<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://arama.hurriyet.com.tr/arsivnews.aspx?id=-599507 |access-date=2008-12-21 |title=Thanks to Nuri Gündeş |work={{le|土耳其自由日報|Turkish Daily News|Turkish Daily News}} |publisher={{le|Hürriyet}} |date=2008-12-21 |first=Mehmet Ali |last=Birand |quote=<!-- It was not the right wing militant and mafia boss Çatlı or mafia boss Çakıcı that finished off the Armenian Secret Army for the Liberation of Armenia (ASALA). They are bragging in vain. -->It was the raid of Paris's Orly Airport in 1983 that finished ASALA off. Feeling ill at ease by the raid, the French and U.S. Armenians who used to support ASALA monetarily stopped the aid and the issue was closed. I know this through French authorities that were involved. The ones that were instrumental in the stopping of the aid were MİT and the Foreign Ministry. Otherwise, ASALA did not yield because it was afraid of the Turkish bullies. They were stopped because they had gone too far with their murders. |archive-date=2013-04-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130418164348/http://arama.hurriyet.com.tr/arsivnews.aspx?id=-599507 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1980年代晚期後，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍因內部分裂與缺乏資金而活躍度大減，但至1990年代還有零星活動，包括1991年對土耳其駐匈牙利大使失敗的攻擊<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tkb.org/Incident.jsp?incID=6723|title=ASALA attacked Diplomatic target|date=1981-12-19|location=Hungary|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070827173744/http://www.tkb.org/Incident.jsp?incID=6723|archive-date=2007-08-27|work={{tsl|en|MIPT Terrorism Knowledge Base|恐怖主義知識資料庫|MIPT Terrorism Knowledge Base}}|accessdate=2021-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及1997年[[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]土耳其駐比利時大使館的爆炸案。此後亞美尼亞解放祕密軍即不再活躍<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/IncidentSummary.aspx?gtdid=199706230005|title=Incident Summary for GTDID: 199706230005|website=www.start.umd.edu|access-date=2019-04-11|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013043/https://www.start.umd.edu/gtd/search/IncidentSummary.aspx?gtdid=199706230005|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭]]中，土耳其與[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]]均指控亞美尼亞招募亞美尼亞解放祕密軍與其盟友[[庫德斯坦工人黨|庫德斯坦工人黨]]的成員參戰<ref>{{Cite web|last=AA|first=DAILY SABAH WITH|date=2020-09-28|title=Armenia deploys PKK, ASALA terrorists to occupied areas, Azerbaijan's envoy to Ankara says|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/politics/diplomacy/armenia-deploys-pkk-asala-terrorists-to-occupied-areas-azerbaijans-envoy-to-ankara-says|access-date=2020-12-28|website=Daily Sabah|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101013106/https://www.dailysabah.com/politics/diplomacy/armenia-deploys-pkk-asala-terrorists-to-occupied-areas-azerbaijans-envoy-to-ankara-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==出版品==
亞美尼亞解放祕密軍出版了許多書籍、手冊與海報等宣傳資料。1980年至1987年、1991年至1997年間，該組織出版期刊《{{le|亞美尼亞 (期刊)|Hayastan (periodical)|亞美尼亞}}》，首期於1980年10月發表於黎巴嫩，共有40頁<ref>Mamule 1967–1980, by Zhirair Danielyan, Haigazian handes, hador T, 1981</ref>。《亞美尼亞》收錄的文章除[[亞美尼亞語|亞美尼亞語]]者外還有[[英語|英語]]、[[法語|法語]]、[[土耳其語|土耳其語]]與[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]的<ref>{{cite book|title=The Armenian Question, encyclopedia|editor=acad. K. Khudaverdyan|year=1996|page=209|chapter =''Hayaqsdan'' |author=A. Sanjian}}</ref>。在[[倫敦|倫敦]]、[[巴黎|巴黎]]也分別有支持者發表與此期刊類似的刊物<ref>{{cite journal|publisher={{le|Spurk}} journal|volume=12|year= 1991|page=32|title=''Hayasdan Gaydzer''}}</ref>。

==書籍==
1980年12月30日，亞美尼亞解放祕密軍在[[西班牙|西班牙]][[馬德里|馬德里]]發動的一次攻擊中，記者{{le|何塞·安東尼奧·古里亞蘭|José Antonio Gurriarán}}在第一枚炸彈爆炸後，馬上聯絡攝影師前來而未即時離開現場，被第二枚炸彈炸傷了雙腿<ref>{{cite web|author=Ángeles García|url=http://elpais.com/diario/1981/02/26/madrid/352038259_850215.html|title=José Antonio Gurriarán, el periodista herido en un atentado armenio: "Me he salvado porque me he negado a morir|publisher=El Pais|date=1981-02-06|language=es|accessdate=2021-01-03|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205165456/https://elpais.com/diario/1981/02/26/madrid/352038259_850215.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=elconfidencial/>，出院後他對該組織的訴求感到好奇，進而至黎巴嫩訪問了幾名該組織的成員<ref name=elconfidencial>{{cite web|url=https://www.elconfidencial.com/cultura/cine/2015-10-27/jose-antonio-gurriaran-la-bomba-mas-poderosa-contra-el-terrorismo-es-el-dialogo_1072432/|title=José Antonio Gurriarán: "La bomba más poderosa contra el terrorismo es el diálogo"|publisher=El Confidencial|date=2015-10-27|language=es|accessdate=2021-01-03|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205165521/https://www.elconfidencial.com/cultura/cine/2015-10-27/jose-antonio-gurriaran-la-bomba-mas-poderosa-contra-el-terrorismo-es-el-dialogo_1072432/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1982年，古里亞蘭出版了《炸彈》（La Bomba）一書，紀錄了他自身經歷爆炸案的經驗、亞美尼亞解放祕密軍的訴求及其背後的歷史<ref name=elconfidencial/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.today/20120730032546/http://www.elpais.com/articulo/ultima/GURRIARaN/_JOSe_ANTONIO_/PERIODISTA/Jose/Antonio/Gurriaran/elpepiult/19820404elpepiult_2/Tes/GENTE |title=José Antonio Gurriarán|publisher=El Pais|date=1982-04-04|language=es}}</ref>。

